function Products() {
    
    const {id, link} = useParams();

    let testArr = [];
    let testArray = [];

    let array = arr.filter((obj) => obj.id == id);
    let arrayed = arr.filter((obj) => obj.type == link);

    testArr.push(array);
    testArray.push(arrayed);

    

    return (

        <Container fluid style={{backgroundColor: "#110B09"}} className="py-5 my-5">
            <Container style={{width: "60%"}} className="d-flex justify-content-center py-5">
                <div style={{width: "50%", height: "100%"}} className="px-3">

                </div>
                <div>
                    {array.map((obj)=>(
                        <PageProductsTitle
                            key={obj.id}
                            colorProduct={obj.productColor} 
                            nameProduct={obj.productName}
                            costProduct={obj.productCost}
                        />
                    ))}
                </div>
            </Container>
        </Container>
    )

}
